{
  "texts": [
    "28 predicted the survival rates of kidney tumors by using DCNN.",
    "Three classes of survival rates 1year, 3years, and5years were produced using their model, with outcomes of 87%, 87%, and 90%, respectively.",
    "They did not extract any patches, which was a computationally intensive process.",
    "They used WSIs as inputs.",
    "Deep survival convolutional network (DeepSurvNet) was introduced by Zadeh Shirazi et al."
  ]
}